
1) Check if git is installed:
git --version

*Use Git Bash

Retrieve a full copy of the repository from GitHub:
git clone [URLCópia]

List All branchs:
git branch

Criar novo branch:
git branch [newbranch]

Set new branch (Checkout) to current branch:
git checkout [newbranch]


*COMMIT PROCESS:

-git status (optional) -> Check the status of working tree

-git add [FILE] -> Move the file from the working tree to the staging area (git add * to stage all files)

